❌ When NOT to Use AWS Lambda
Case	                        Why Not
Long-running tasks (>15 min)	Max timeout = 15 min
Heavy CPU / Memory jobs	        Limited compute
Constant background jobs	    Very expensive
Stateful applications	        Lambda is stateless
Very low latency systems	    Cold start delay
